Interface ReadDivisionService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultReadDivisionService

    public interface ReadDivisionService

    This service enables you to display revision master data to be consumed in SAP Fiori apps and on other user interfaces.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_DIVISION_SRV
    API Version:1
    Communication Scenario:SAP Business Objects Cloud for Planning Integration (SAP_COM_0087)
    Scope Items:oData Integration with SAP Business Objects Cloud for Planning (1YB)
